  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Counter-Poaching Training Programme for Sub-Saharan Africa</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to reduce poaching of rhino and elephant within specific protected areas in sub-Saharan Africa, by significantly improving parks&#x2019; law enforcement capacity. Training will be provided to rangers in proven tracking tactics. Additional training in information gathering and analysis - and the establishment of an information network between protected areas - will improve coordination of national and international efforts to disrupt illegal wildlife trade.</narrative>
  </description>
